      "n": 25,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet kad tee prett ſawo Tehwo Deewu apgrehkojahs/ un teem Deeweem to Seimmes Lauſchu pakkaž maukoja/ ko Deews wizzu Preekſcha bij iſdeldejs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad paniokdinaja tas Iſraēta Deews Wuhla ta Affirijas Kehnina Garru/un to Garru TiglatPilleſſera ta Affirijas Kehnina/ un tas aiſwedde tohs Ruhbeniterus/ un Gaddite.rus/ un to puſs Zilti Manaſſus Zeetuma/ un nowedde to uhs Alu/ un Aboru/ un Arn/ un pee Gosana Uppes lihds ſchodcen.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta VII. Nodalla.\nLewja Behrnu Raddu. Rafsti: 1. To paſchu Kalpoſchanas/ Pilſſahti un Dſhwoschanas: 31/ 54.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ee Behrnt Lewja btja/ Gersous/ Kaāts/ un Merarus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Kaāta Behrni btja/ Amrans/ Jezears/ un Eebrons/ un Uſiels.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Amrains Behrnt btja/ Aārons un Mohsus/ un Mirjame. Un Aārona Behrnt btja/ Nadabs/ un Abijus/ Eeleasars/ un Ihtamars.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Eeleasars dſeendinaja Ptueafu. Pineas dſeendinaja Abisui.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Abisuus dſeendinaja\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Usus dſeendinaja Seraju. Un Serajus dſeendinaja Mrajotu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Merajots dſeendinaja martiju. Un Amartius dſeminaja Akitabu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Akitabs dſemdina Zadaku. Un Zadaks dſemdina Akimaāzu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Akimaāz dſemdina Asariju. Un Asarijus dſeminaja Joananu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Joanans dſemdina Asarijn/to/ kaž par Preestert ja tai Namma/ ko Salama Jeruſalewenē uſtaſiija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Asarijus dſemdina Amariju. Un Amarijus dſeminaja Akitabu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Akitabs dſemdina Zadaku. Un Zadaks dſemdina Sallumu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Sallums dſemdina Jktiju. Un Jktijus dſemdina Asartju.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Asartjus dſemdina Seraju. Un Serajus dſeminaja Jozadakn.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet Jozadaks btja lihd kad tas KUNGS Juhdu Jeruſalemi aiſwedde zaur bukad Nezara Rohku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad nu tee Behrni Lewirr/ Gersons/ Kaāts/ un Merarus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ſchee irr Gerso Behrnu Wahrdi: Libnus Simejus.\n"
    }
  ],
